account.descriptionLink: Moodeng Fans Club is dedicated to enhancing Moodeng's well-being. Join us on January 12 for our first DAO proposal vote through Solana's Realms. If approved, 5% of our $MS holdings will be allocated to improve Moodeng's diet, living conditions, and security in her habitat starting January 13. Let’s make a difference together!
account.name: Improving Moodeng’s Life: Community Announcement
